Ibato rematongerwe enyika riri munyika [[Zimbabwe|yeZimbabwe]]. Parizvino bato iri inotungamirirwa na Va [[Morgan Tsvangirai]], uye nderimwe ramapato matatu ari muhurumende yemubatanidzwa iri kutungamirirwa naBaba VaMugabe. Bato reMDC rakavambwa mugore ra1998 uye varume vana vakatungamirira kuvamba bato iri vanoti Learnmore Jongwe, Tafadzwa Musekiwa, Morgan Tsvangirai na Job Sikhala. Sikhala wakakurira kwaKangera muZaka. Jongwe wakazofa plus Sikhala wakamboinda kwaMutambara asi wakazodzingwa totally.

